Net discover:
 - sudo netdiscover ip
for range 
- sudo netdiscover -r myip

create directory and touch file target and store the output.

NSE - nmap Scripting Engine
- to scan prebuild vulnerability.

verbosity  --> -v

- sudo netdiscover 172.1.42.44/16
- export target=172.1.42.44        
- nmap $target -p1-65535 -v -min-rate=3000
-p range
-v Increase verbosity level (use -vv or more for greater effect)
- nmap $target -p1-65535 -v -min-rate=3000 -Pn => to skip host discovery(Pn)
- nmap $target -p1-65535 -v -min-rate=3000 -oN filename.txt => to save the output

                                
